race.comment: ASEVENTY SEVEN (1) looks the one to beat. Won two on end then finished fourth at Caulfield Heath in much tougher company. Well placed back in this class and expected to bounce back. FINE REBEL (10) finds it hard to win with just two from 38 but has been racing well. Not far away when fifth last time in similar grade and looks a strong win chance this line-up. LUMPYS HIGHWAY (4) hasn't been far off in the last two, the latest third at Yarra Valley over 1968m. Overdue and should be winding up strongly.  ELEGANT MAN (5) was stepping put over 1800m for the first time and was as sent forward, scoring won his maiden success at Kerang. May relish the extra trip here and expected to give a sight again.
